Package guardians.model.dtos.scheduler

This package contains the DTO classes used to expose information to the Scheduler

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbsenceSchedulerDTO
    This DTO will represent the information related to an Absence exposed to the scheduler

    This DTO represents the information related to an AllowedShift exposed to the scheduler
    CalendarSchedulerDTO
    This class represents the information related to a Calendar that is exposed to the scheduler
